{"tid":979901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被尼龍網勒頸出血 悲傷海豹震驚世人","createTime":"2019-01-13T05:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T06:09:11.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07a633a3a6bec5f877af1bbca555cf4ff7712a73","tid":979901,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4FioRkX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4FioRkX.png&h=14f2ac07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國攝影師馬克羅（Paul Macro），近日在諾福克郡海灘上拍到一張震驚各界的照片，那就是一隻雌海豹被尼龍網勒頸勒到出血，臉上表情無比悲傷。<br />\n <br />\n綜合外媒報導，馬克羅為了製作年度日曆，因此到海邊拍攝海豹的照片，正當他沿著沙灘搜尋時，就看到了被尼龍網纏住脖頸的海豹。馬克羅隨即找來動物救援組織幫忙，但最後這隻受傷的雌海豹依舊喪命。<br />\n <br />\n英國諾福克郡金斯林（Kings Lynn）東溫奇野生動物中心經理查爾斯（Alison Charles）表示，志工們都很希望馬上為海豹解危，但結果令人沮喪。<br />\n <br />\n去年，在諾福克海灘上有5隻海豹脖子被飛盤套住，迄今世界各地有許多種動物都因為塑膠廢棄物而死亡，動物組織呼籲民眾若在海灘見到垃圾，應在能力所即的範圍內協助清除。"},{"pid":"d5264aedc9d741458a0fa6d30dbecd367967ca69","tid":979901,"uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:56:10.000Z","msg":"走塑要走埋尼龍繩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df21f63546f1a369bb66dcb58761cea59259784","tid":979901,"uid":155137,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:01:40.000Z","msg":"屌那星 邊間鋪再賣尼龍制品誅九族"},{"pid":"6246afbffe37806428787e3a3e8b0a50394bd185","tid":979901,"uid":1255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"幾時&quot;走人&quot;??"},{"pid":"df79f3c7da7e04ad097e1954c7d9fc2250d64101","tid":979901,"uid":50935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"以為海豹突擊隊用尼龍殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1430cff27dc4697ff87795a646572d5a3d22c754","tid":979901,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:05:52.000Z","msg":"禁得絲襪未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8dba6a1c9a0eb2cf4e687aabd47ea102bf0d1d","tid":979901,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"nike addi u記要執粒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b79100de8ac402a0e53813451d740e7da1277e","tid":979901,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"海豹個樣好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}